data.description: Welcome to your ideal one-level oasis! Nestled in a serene neighborhood on a cul-de-sac with covered front entry. This charming 3-bed, 2-bath home offers a perfect blend of comfort and functionality. Step inside to discover an inviting layout bathed in natural light, where every corner reflects modern elegance and thoughtful design. The heart of the home, a generous living area, beckons you to unwind or entertain with ease. Adjacent, a stylishly appointed kitchen awaits, boasting granite countertops, ample cabinetry, and premium appliance. Retreat to the tranquil master suite, complete with a private ensuite bath and walk in closet.
